race.description: Federal Hotel (N/P) Mixed Series F Pr2 Division1
race.comment: SEAN'S MATILDA (2) held her own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only half a length (30.20) behind Magic Nancy at this track. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Good form should continue. BOURNE DEXSTAR (1) was in the money two back in a TG1-4W at this track then jumped from a squeeze draw last time and was not far away when third (23.45) over 400m at this track. Well placed here and can atone this time. MAGIC POPPY (8) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (23.30) in a TG1-4W at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from seven starts. Should be thereabouts.
